  • Method Details

    • onActionGenerateSchedule

      public void onActionGenerateSchedule(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent)
      This method displays contact-specific appointments in a table view. The user selects a contact from a combo-box which populates the table view with their associated appointments.
      Parameters:
      actionEvent - The selection of a contact in a combo-box.

    • onActionGenerateTotals

      public void onActionGenerateTotals(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent)
      This method displays the total appointments for each month in a bar chart. The user inputs a year into a text-field. which populates the chart with the totals for each month in that year.
      Parameters:
      actionEvent - Pressing the submit button after entering a year into the text-field.

    • onActionGenerateType

      public void onActionGenerateType(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent)
      This method displays the total of appointments for a given month and type.
      Parameters:
      actionEvent - Pressing the submit button after a selection is made in the type and month combo-boxes.

    • onActionReturn
